title: Renament Gastrobar
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Thai, Mediterranean, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu changes and is based on seasonal products. Specializes in lunch, breakfast, coffee and drinks. Vegetarian items include tom kha, green curry, yellow curry, red curry, matsaman curry, pad thai, pad see ew, khao neeo; vegans please inquire as to which might be or can be made vegan. A  vegan baoburger is available.
